  "full_text": "A mother and daughter with Gorlin syndrome with similar neuroradiological findings are reported. These include calcification of the falx cerebri and tentorium cerebelli and dysgenesis of the corpus callosum and vermis. Vermian dysgenesis was detected in both mother and daughter suggesting a previously unrecognized finding associated with Gorlin syndrome.",
